post_text: Thank you for supporting Rock Creek Schools The Alms Group !
shared_text:
The Alms Group Real Estate
May 10, 2018 at 3:00 AM ·

In the past week, our team has been completely blown away by everyone's nominations and support for our local teachers! We started The Alms Group because we care about supporting education in our community. It's clear from your nominations that our educators are making an unbelievable impact on our kids and deserve much more recognition than we could ever give. Selecting our six teachers was nearly impossible and we sincerely thank every single teacher that was nominated! We are pleased to announce that the following six teachers have been selected to receive funding for their classroom projects:

Kelly Carmody
Joyce Maxwell Eckelberry
Molly Ellen Emert
Rachael Herzog Hoeme
Steve LaRocque
Erin Meyer

Thank you to everyone for sharing your incredible nominations! We will be in touch with these six teachers and keep you posted on their continued impact on education in our community!
